window.bookSummaryJSON = "Following the success of the mass market original <i>Forgotten</i> comes the second book in the Mercy Street series. A new pulse-stopping thriller from wildly popular <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Mariah Stewart. <p> A beautiful co-ed mysteriously disappears from her sorority house, and the Mercy Street Foundation is summoned to find her -- the first investigation for a brilliant crime scene analyst and a first forensic psychologist. </p> <p>Stewart's last three series have all seen millions of books in print and her sales are surging. There are over 1.3 million copies in print of the Truth series, and her Last trilogy went to press numerous times.</p>"; 
